======================================

1. ATTACK ITEMS (Physical Damage)
==================================

Tier 1 (Basic):
- Dagger: Basic physical attack damage
- Expert Glove: Hybrid adaptive attack for all roles
- Iron Hunting Bow: Physical attack + cooldown reduction
- Javelin: Critical chance for crit builds
- Knive: Attack speed for trinity builds
- Vampire Mallet: Physical attack + lifesteal for sustain

Tier 2 (Intermediate):
- Fury Hammer: Physical attack + physical penetration
- Legion Sword: High physical attack damage
- Ogre Tomahawk: Physical attack + HP (for fighters)
- Regular Spear: Physical attack + attack speed
- Rogue Meteor: Attack speed + critical chance
- Magic Blade: Physical attack + lifesteal + shield on low HP
- Swift Crossbow: Attack speed with dual passives

Tier 3 (Core/Late Game):
- Berserker's Fury: Critical damage + critical chance (core for crit builds)
- Blade of Despair: Highest physical attack + bonus damage to low HP enemies
- Blade of the Heptaseas: Burst damage + penetration + slow on next basic attack
- Corrosion Scythe: Attack speed + slow effect (core for trinity builds)
- Demon Hunter Sword: % HP damage against tanks + lifesteal
- Endless Battle: True damage after skill + hybrid lifesteal (fighter core)
- Fleeting Time: Ultimate cooldown reduction on kills/assists (cross-category)
- Golden Staff: Convert crit chance to attack speed + DPS increase
- Great Dragon Spear: Movement speed + crit chance after ultimate
- Haas' Claws: High lifesteal + critical chance (marksman sustain)
- Hunter Strike: Cooldown reduction + movement speed after damage
- Malefic Gun: Basic attack range extension + penetration
- Malefic Roar: High physical penetration vs tanks
- Rose Gold Meteor: Shield + hybrid defense when low HP
- Sea Halberd: Anti-heal + anti-shield (vs sustain heroes)
- Sky Piercer: Stacking execute damage on kills (snowball item)
- War Axe: Stacking damage + penetration + spell vamp in fights
- Wind of Nature: Physical immunity + lifesteal (vs physical damage)
- Windtalker: Chain lightning effect + attack speed + crit


2. MAGIC ITEMS (Magic Damage)
==============================

Tier 1 (Basic):
- Book of Sages: Magic power + cooldown reduction
- Expert Glove: Hybrid adaptive attack
- Magic Necklace: Mana regeneration (early game sustain)
- Mystery Codex: Magic power boost
- Power Crystal: Maximum mana increase

Tier 2 (Intermediate):
- Exotic Veil: Magic power + movement speed
- Magic Wand: Significant magic power boost
- Mystic Container: Magic power + spell vamp
- Tome of Evil: Magic power + mana regen + cooldown reduction
- Azure Blade: Mana regen + cooldown reduction (for supports)
- Elegant Gem: HP + mana + heal on level up

Tier 3 (Core/Late Game):
- Blood Wings: Shield based on magic power + movement speed
- Clock of Destiny: Stacking HP + magic power + defense over time
- Concentrated Energy: Hybrid lifesteal + HP (mage sustain)
- Divine Glaive: % magic penetration vs high magic defense tanks
- Enchanted Talisman: High cooldown reduction + mana regen (skill spam)
- Feather of Heaven: Basic attack magic damage + attack speed (for attack-based mages)
- Flask of the Oasis: Healing/shield power boost + anti-burst (support core)
- Fleeting Time: Ultimate cooldown reduction on kills/assists
- Genius Wand: Flat magic penetration + reduces enemy magic defense
- Glowing Wand: Burn damage + anti-heal + HP-based damage
- Holy Crystal: Percent magic power increase (late game burst)
- Ice Queen Wand: Slow effect on magic damage + spell vamp
- Lightning Truncheon: AoE burst chain lightning based on mana
- Sky Piercer: Stacking execute damage (cross-category)
- Starlium Scythe: True damage on basic attacks after skills (magic assassin core)
- Winter Crown: Active invincibility + freeze (defensive)
- Wishing Lantern: Bonus magic damage based on enemy HP


3. DEFENSE ITEMS (Survival)
============================

Tier 1 (Basic):
- Healing Necklace: HP regeneration (passive sustain)
- Hero's Ring: HP + cooldown reduction
- Leather Jerkin: Physical defense (builds into armor items)
- Magic Resist Cloak: Magic defense (builds into magic resist items)
- Vitality Crystal: HP increase (builds into HP items)

Tier 2 (Intermediate):
- Ares Belt: Large HP increase
- Silence Robe: HP + magic defense
- Steel Legplates: Physical defense
- Black Ice Shield: Hybrid defense + defense aura
- Dreadnought Armor: Hybrid defense + damage reduction (vs physical burst)
- Molten Essence: HP + AoO burning damage (for lane clear)

Tier 3 (Core/Late Game):
- Antique Cuirass: HP + physical defense + reduces enemy physical attack
- Athena's Shield: Magic defense + shield vs magic burst
- Blade Armor: Reflects basic attack damage + crit damage reduction (vs marksmen)
- Brute Force Breastplate: Stacking defense + damage + movement speed + tenacity
- Chastise Pauldron: HP + physical defense + reduces enemy attack speed
- Cursed Helmet: HP + magic defense + AoE burning damage
- Dominance Ice: Physical defense + mana + anti-heal aura + slow
- Fleeting Time: Ultimate cooldown reduction (cross-category)
- Guardian Helmet: Massive HP + high regeneration (sustain tank core)
- Immortality: Revive on death (late game survival)
- Oracle: HP + hybrid defense + increases all shields/healing received
- Queen's Wings: Spell vamp + damage reduction when low HP (fighter sustain)
- Radiant Armor: Magic defense + stacking protection vs continuous magic damage
- Thunder Belt: True damage on basic attacks + slow + permanent defense stacking
- Rock Potion: HP + damage reduction (consumable, no slot needed)


4. MOVEMENT ITEMS (Boots)
==========================

Tier 1:
- Boots: Basic movement speed (all heroes)

Tier 2 (Specialized Boots):
- Arcane Boots: Movement speed + magic power + flat magic penetration (for mages)
- Demon Shoes: Movement speed + mana regen (for mana-hungry mages/supports)
- Magic Shoes: Movement speed + cooldown reduction + HP (for skill-spam heroes)
- Rapid Boots: High movement speed out of combat (for roamers/rotators)
- Swift Boots: Movement speed + attack speed (for marksmen/attack speed heroes)
- Tough Boots: Movement speed + magic defense + reduces CC duration (vs crowd control)
- Warrior Boots: Movement speed + physical defense + stacking defense when hit (vs physical lane)

Special Items (0 Gold - Utility):
- Throw Forbidden: Prevents allied Jawhead from throwing your hero
- Allow Throw: Reverts Throw Forbidden effect
- Broken Heart: Prevents Carmilla from being pulled by Cecilion
- Resonating Heart: Reverts Broken Heart effect


5. JUNGLING ITEMS
=================

Hunter's Knife: Basic jungling item - required to deal bonus damage to creeps

Retribution Upgrades (Blessings on Boots):
- Ice Retribution: Retribution slows enemies + deals true damage
- Bloody Retribution: Retribution deals damage + heals the user
- Flame Retribution: Retribution deals damage + burns enemies

Jungle Blessings:
- Beast Killer: Gain stacks when killing creeps + bonus true damage to creeps
- Star Shard: Gain bonus gold from creeps + adaptive attack
- Wooden Mask: Gain bonus experience + HP regen when near allies


6. ROAMING ITEMS
================

Roaming Blessings (upgraded from boots):
- Conceal: Active - Grants invisibility + movement speed to nearby allies
- Encourage: Passive - Increases damage of nearby allies
- Favor: Passive - Heals nearby allies when assisting or killing
- Dire Hit: Passive - Increases damage to low HP enemies

Roaming Items:
- Roaming Boots: Base roaming item - gain assist gold without stealing lane gold
- Flask of the Oasis: Support item - increases healing/shielding power + prevents burst damage


=======================================
QUICK REFERENCE: CORE ITEMS BY ROLE
=======================================

Marksman (Gold Lane):
   Swift Boots, Berserker's Fury, Haas' Claws, Malefic Gun, Wind of Nature, Demon Hunter Sword

Assassin (Jungle):
   Hunter's Knife, Blade of Heptaseas, Hunter Strike, Sky Piercer, Blade of Despair, Endless Battle

Fighter (EXP Lane):
   Warrior/Tough Boots, War Axe, Queen's Wings, Hunter Strike, Blade of Despair

Tank (Roam):
   Tough/Warrior Boots, Dominance Ice, Athena's Shield, Antique Cuirass, Guardian Helmet, Immortality

Mage (Mid Lane):
   Arcane Boots, Genius Wand, Glowing Wand, Holy Crystal, Divine Glaive, Lightning Truncheon

Support (Roam):
   Demon/Magic Shoes, Flask of the Oasis, Enchanted Talisman, Fleeting Time, Oracle


